  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate", 
    "date": "2014-09-18T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Exercise and Fitness For All Act - Directs the Access Board\u00a0to develop and publish guidelines for exercise or fitness service providers to provide accessible exercise or fitness equipment, including relevant personnel training. Requires such guidelines to ensure that exercise or fitness equipment is accessible to, and usable by, individuals with disabilities.\n\nAmends the Internal Revenue Code to allow eligible small businesses a tax credit for providing accessible exercise or fitness equipment for use by individuals with disabilities."
  }, 
